title: Trouble Kidd Talks Being Born In Mexico, Getting Shot, Spanish Rap and More
description:
Doknow chops it up with Trouble Kidd about his upbringing, his come up, and more! ----- 00:00 Intro 6:24 - Face tats, Moms tripping on him about it and kicking him out, not blaming his parents for his decisions 8:09 - Getting sh*t in the I.E, his mom finding out, getting out the hospital the same day 10:05 - Starting to rap while being locked up, his mom getting him a studio for when he got out jail, mixing and mastering his own music 12:27 - His first song went viral 14:41 - Working a roofing job when song went rival 19:13 - Not worrying about his love life, focusing on getting bread, making love songs, women being the best fans 26:37 - Keeping the homies name alive through his music 27:29 - Working with G Perico, being a fan of his, doing the music video in LA, getting a rare feature with Ohgeesy 30:40 - Using Tik Tok to promote the music 32:35 - Top 5 Latino artists coming up, Oxnard artist 36:20 - New songs with Ohgeesy, Rucci ----- NO JUMPER PATREON http://www.patreon.com/nojumper CHECK OUT OUR NEW SPOTIFY PLAYLIST https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5te...
